PACKAGING
=========

- Background daemon on Linux and Maemo
  As a user, I want the moled daemon to run in the background and on
  startup, and to generate useable logs that can help with debugging.
  DOD: A package that does this.  When moled is run as root, put HOME
  file in different place (not ~root)

  Priority: Low
  Complexity: C2
  Date assigned: Oct 26 2010
  
- Local Development and Testing
  As a developer, I want to be able to run a local version easily.
  DOD: Ability to point client at alternative server simply; passwords
  are not in code; run server anywhere

  Priority: High
  Complexity: C1
  Date assigned: Oct 26 2010
  Date completed: Oct 29 2010

